7054.text: [7054] StaticText " archive can be used to subscribe to any combination of existing physics archives, e.g. to something like `General Relativity', `Astrophysics', and `High Energy Physics - Experimental'. This is also the only way to subscribe to a subset of the subject classes within the "

'
